# Benchmark results: track ONLY explicitly-redacted, shareable results (`*.redacted.json`).
# Full results MUST be named `*.unredacted.json` (never a bare `*.json`) so intent is explicit
# and an unmarked file can never be mistaken for safe-to-share. Unredacted results and derived
# summaries are local-only: they can contain host-identifying detail and are large.
*
!.gitignore
!*.redacted.json
